## How to Run
To start the app, run:

```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```

If the app is already running, you may need to stop it (Ctrl+C) and run it again to see the changes if they don't hot-reload correctly. 
Once running, click the **"Start Camera"** checkbox to begin tracking.
